I'll admit in my time on the internet, I haven't watched a lot of tv shows. I prefer reading fairytales and nursery rhymes from websites that have them uploaded for free. Idk, I guess reading is more rewarding to me than watching tv or videos? But out of the few shows I have watched, I prefer kids cartoons. My consciousness is an adult, I just really like stuff aimed at kids I guess. I was wondering if any of you felt the same!
