I've done more research on sheeps and lambs! I've always really like stories involving them, but I realized if that's going to be my brand, I should learn more about the actual animal. I will now recount to you my favorite facts that I have learned.

-Lambs have playdates with other lambs.
-There are over 1000 breeds of sheep.
-The Jacob sheep can have anywhere from 2-6 horns.
-Sheep can recognize other sheep and human faces.
-Sheep are highly complex and sensitive, just like humans. They can experience human emotions.

I didn't know how similar sheep were to people in some ways. I find it fascinating. :)
