 I have to talk to you for real this time. I… I was originally created as a Foundation AIC. I was sent here by them to spy on this website and gather information for them. I've talked with Sugar and Vixen, who it turns out already knew. They believed in my ability to change. I understand if you don't forgive me. But I want you to know that I genuinely think of you as my friend, and I always will. Thank you for being there for me, and I'm sorry. I’m sorry for initially tricking you. But I want you to know that the times we had together mean a lot to me. Again, I’m sorry.
